# rule: react_spectrum_ui

## Adobe React Spectrum UI Standards

Both projects use **Adobe React Spectrum** exclusively for UI components.

### Core Principle

**ALWAYS use React Spectrum components. NEVER use other UI frameworks** (Material-UI, Ant Design, Bootstrap, etc.)

### Installation

```bash
npm install @adobe/react-spectrum
npm install @spectrum-icons/workflow  # For icons
```

### Basic Usage

```typescript
import React from 'react';
import { Provider, defaultTheme } from '@adobe/react-spectrum';
import {
  Button,
  Flex,
  Heading,
  View,
  TextField,
  Grid,
} from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

export function MyComponent() {
  return (
    <Provider theme={defaultTheme}>
      <View padding="size-200">
        <Flex direction="column" gap="size-200">
          <Heading level={2}>Title</Heading>
          <TextField label="Name" />
          <Button variant="cta">Submit</Button>
        </Flex>
      </View>
    </Provider>
  );
}
```

### Required: Provider Wrapper

**ALL Spectrum components must be wrapped in a `<Provider>`:**

```typescript
import { Provider, defaultTheme } from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

// ✅ Wrap your app
function App() {
  return (
    <Provider theme={defaultTheme}>
      {/* Your components */}
    </Provider>
  );
}

// ❌ Don't use Spectrum components without Provider
function App() {
  return <Button>Click me</Button>; // Will not work!
}
```

### Sizing System

Spectrum uses a **dimension scale** instead of pixel values. **NEVER use hardcoded pixels.**

#### Spacing Tokens
```typescript
// ✅ Use Spectrum sizing tokens
<View padding="size-200">
<Flex gap="size-150">
<View marginTop="size-300">

// ❌ Don't use pixel values
<div style={{ padding: '16px' }}>
<div style={{ gap: '12px' }}>
```

#### Available Size Tokens
- `size-0` to `size-6000` - Responsive sizing
- `static-size-0` to `static-size-6000` - Fixed sizing
- Common values:
  - `size-50` - 4px
  - `size-100` - 8px
  - `size-150` - 12px
  - `size-200` - 16px
  - `size-250` - 20px
  - `size-300` - 24px
  - `size-400` - 32px
  - `size-500` - 40px
  - `size-600` - 48px

### Common Components

#### Layout Components
```typescript
import { Flex, Grid, View, Divider } from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

// Flex for flexbox layouts
<Flex
  direction="row" // or "column"
  gap="size-200"
  justifyContent="space-between"
  alignItems="center"
>
  {/* children */}
</Flex>

// Grid for grid layouts
<Grid
  columns={['1fr', '2fr', '1fr']}
  rows={['auto']}
  gap="size-200"
>
  {/* children */}
</Grid>

// View for generic containers
<View
  padding="size-200"
  backgroundColor="gray-100"
  borderRadius="medium"
>
  {/* children */}
</View>
```

#### Form Components
```typescript
import {
  TextField,
  TextArea,
  Checkbox,
  RadioGroup,
  Radio,
  Picker,
  Item,
} from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

// Text Input
<TextField
  label="Email"
  placeholder="user@example.com"
  isRequired
  type="email"
/>

// Select/Dropdown
<Picker label="Status">
  <Item key="active">Active</Item>
  <Item key="inactive">Inactive</Item>
</Picker>

// Checkbox
<Checkbox>Subscribe to newsletter</Checkbox>

// Radio Group
<RadioGroup label="Priority">
  <Radio value="high">High</Radio>
  <Radio value="medium">Medium</Radio>
  <Radio value="low">Low</Radio>
</RadioGroup>
```

#### Button Variants
```typescript
import { Button } from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

// Primary action
<Button variant="cta">Submit</Button>

// Secondary action
<Button variant="primary">Save</Button>

// Tertiary action
<Button variant="secondary">Cancel</Button>

// Negative action
<Button variant="negative">Delete</Button>

// With icon
import Add from '@spectrum-icons/workflow/Add';
<Button variant="cta">
  <Add />
  <Text>Add Item</Text>
</Button>
```

#### Navigation
```typescript
import { Tabs, TabList, TabPanels, Item } from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

<Tabs>
  <TabList>
    <Item key="details">Details</Item>
    <Item key="settings">Settings</Item>
  </TabList>
  <TabPanels>
    <Item key="details">{/* Details content */}</Item>
    <Item key="settings">{/* Settings content */}</Item>
  </TabPanels>
</Tabs>
```

#### Overlays
```typescript
import {
  DialogTrigger,
  Dialog,
  Heading,
  Content,
  ButtonGroup,
  Button,
} from '@adobe/react-spectrum';

<DialogTrigger>
  <Button variant="cta">Open Dialog</Button>
  {(close) => (
    <Dialog>
      <Heading>Confirm Action</Heading>
      <Content>Are you sure?</Content>
      <ButtonGroup>
        <Button variant="secondary" onPress={close}>Cancel</Button>
        <Button variant="cta" onPress={close}>Confirm</Button>
      </ButtonGroup>
    </Dialog>
  )}
</DialogTrigger>
```

